snippet.textDisplay:
Lots of people asking why CS Pakistan is able to connect so much better with the public than say CS India. The very short answer to this is our lack of a film industry for example Bollywood.

Over the last several decades Pakistani indie artists have had to work very hard for very little return. The results are now very visible thanks especially to the internets.

I did not decide which side of the imaginary line to be born into and neither did you. 

🫂
